-2024-07-08/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 10:32:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-07-08/</guid></item><item><title>德国商报报道，ASML 首席执行官表示世界需要中国生产的传统芯片</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/asml-ceo-says-world-needs-legacy-chips-china-is-producing-handelsblatt-reports-2024-07-08/</link><description>设备制造商ASML首席执行官在周一发表的德国商报采访中表示，包括德国汽车行业在内的芯片买家需要中国芯片制造商目前正在投资的老一代计算机芯片。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 10:08:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/asml-ceo-says-world-needs-legacy-chips-china-is-producing-handelsblatt-reports-2024-07-08/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯官员称美国离开武器条约是为了制造武器威胁中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/russian-official-says-us-left-arms-treaty-build-weapons-menace-china-2024-07-08/</link><description>俄罗斯副外长谢尔盖·里亚布科夫周一指责美国决定退出苏联时代的军控条约，以便华盛顿可以开始制造武器来恐吓中国。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 10:01:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/russian-official-says-us-left-arms-treaty-build-weapons-menace-china-2024-07-08/</guid></item><item><title>摩根大通下调新兴市场企业违约预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/jpmorgan-cuts-forecast-emerging-market-corporate-defaults-2024-07-08/</link><description>继陷入困境的市场定价出现自 2016 年以来的最大改善后，投资银行摩根大通周一下调了对预计出现债务违约的新兴市场公司数量的预测。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 10:01:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/jpmorgan-cuts-forecast-emerging-market-corporate-defaults-2024-07-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国称菲律宾军舰“损坏”南海环礁珊瑚礁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-claims-philippine-warships-damaged-reef-atoll-south-china-sea-2024-07-08/</link><description>中国周一表示，菲律宾军舰在南海南沙群岛“非法”搁浅，“严重破坏”了该地区的珊瑚礁生态系统，两国在这片广阔水道的环礁上存在争议领土。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 09:53:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-claims-philippine-warships-damaged-reef-atoll-south-china-sea-2024-07-08/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，印度将于7月试行从蒙古进口炼焦煤</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/india-get-coking-coal-mongolia-trial-basis-july-sources-say-2024-07-08/</link><description>两名知情人士称，印度将从本月晚些时候开始试行从蒙古进口炼焦煤，新德里寻求实现关键炼钢原材料进口多元化，以减少对澳大利亚的过度依赖。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 09:46:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/india-get-coking-coal-mongolia-trial-basis-july-sources-say-2024-07-08/</guid></item><item><title>匈牙利寻求跨国公司、银行、能源部门的“国防贡献”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/hungary-seeking-defence-contribution-multinational-firms-banks-energy-sector-2024-07-08/</link><description>匈牙利总理欧尔班·维克多的幕僚长周一表示，匈牙利政府将寻求银行、能源公司和跨国公司的“国防贡献”。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 09:42:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/hungary-seeking-defence-contribution-multinational-firms-banks-energy-sector-2024-07-08/</guid></item><item><title>克里姆林宫表示俄罗斯赞赏匈牙利澄清俄乌冲突立场的努力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/kremlin-says-russia-appreciates-hungary-efforts-clarify-positions-russia-ukraine-2024-07-08/</link><description>克里姆林宫周一表示，俄罗斯赞赏匈牙利总理欧尔班·维克托为澄清俄罗斯和乌克兰在解决冲突问题上的立场所做的努力。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 09:39:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/kremlin-says-russia-appreciates-hungary-efforts-clarify-positions-russia-ukraine-2024-07-08/</guid></item><item><title>行业机构官员表示，欧盟关税打击了中国电动汽车出口的增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-car-sales-slide-june-falling-third-month-2024-07-08/</link><description>中国一家领先汽车行业机构的一位官员周一表示，欧洲关税的前景将使中国近几个月电动和插电式混合动力汽车出口增长下降20-30个百分点。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 08:11:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-car-sales-slide-june-falling-third-month-2024-07-08/</guid></item><item><title>匈牙利总理在与中国国家主席习近平会谈后前往华盛顿</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/hungarys-pm-travels-washington-after-talks-with-chinas-xi-2024-07-08/</link><description>匈牙利总理维克托·欧尔班周一表示，他在北京讨论了中国对乌克兰的和平计划后将前往华盛顿。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 08:00:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/hungarys-pm-travels-washington-after-talks-with-chinas-xi-2024-07-08/</guid></item><item><title>当地媒体称，中国可能调查储能电站的火灾风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-may-investigate-energy-storage-plants-fire-risks-local-media-says-2024-07-08/</link><description>据《21世纪经济报道》周一报道，中国当局正在考虑下令对储能工厂进行大规模火灾风险调查，这表明中国蓬勃发展的电池储能行业标准更加严格。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 07:21:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-may-investigate-energy-storage-plants-fire-risks-local-media-says-2024-07-08/</guid></item><item><title>早盘：法军左翼包抄右翼</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-07-08/</link><description>韦恩·科尔 (Wayne Cole) 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 04:35:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-07-08/</guid></item></channel></rss>